        <updateDate>2022-04-28T21:34:30Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Save American Baseball Act</strong></p> <p>This bill removes the limited exemption from the antitrust laws for persons in the business of organized professional baseball. For purposes of this bill, the term <em>antitrust laws</em> means laws to protect against unlawful restraints and monopolies (Clayton Act) and to protect against unfair methods of competition (Federal Trade Commission Act).</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
